Dear Papa I long to see you.\'a0 I want you to bring my knife & puppy.\'a0 I expect when you come back I will be far in my book.\'a0 Today Ma sent me & Anna & Frank in the piazza to bring in one log of wood.\'a0 Frank brought in one log, & I brought in an arm full & one log besides.\'a0 Lindy is gone to the farm to\'85Maria.\'a0 Mr. Erwin says I am the best boy in school.\'a0 Tell Mr. Summer howdye.\'a0 I hope you will come back safe.\'a0 Have you got your cake yet?\'a0 I hope you got it safe.\'a0 I hope you will get my letter safe.\'a0 Goodbye Papa.\'a0 Your affectionate son Willie.\
