\'a0\
Dear Papa\
\'a0\
\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 I wrote to Mama yesterday, & I will write you a few lines today.\'a0 I received your letter yesterday & one also from Mama at the same time.\'a0 Hers was dated the 5
