\fs29\fsmilli14667 \nosupersub  Jany.\'a0 He would have gone down immediately, but all business men ought to be at home Sale Day, & he could not return in time.\'a0 So you will soon see him, & I expect Willie.\'a0 Write every day.\'a0 Your affectionate Mother, E.F.P.\'a0\'a0\
